Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:35.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be dangerous to ignore the enemy base ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:40.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will fly reconnaissance in order to locate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:42.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Messis{\i0} will serve as your relay station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:45.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,And what should we do when we find the base ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you judge that the circumstances—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:52.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Under the circumstances, we should completely annihilate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you were taken off the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:12.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's something that might be the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't say. I promised not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:28.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:35.80,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sibylla
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru always does whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sir, are you sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:52.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, I sometimes wonder what those sibyllae are thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Really," indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:59.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,If only I could follow my passions as wholeheartedly as she does...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Where is that Simoun going?\N— Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru and Sibylla Yun, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see. Sibylla Aaeru and Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:42.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,After Chor Rubor was dissolved, these two sibyllae were assigned to the {\i1}Messis{\i0} as your replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've been conducting reconnaissance missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all we can do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've heard what happened to Dominura and Limone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,But where are Aaeru and Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:04:00.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two... won't be participating in this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, yes. I'm sure we can discuss the reasons for that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:08.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll go over the details of the operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,but first you should get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know it's a bit early, but I'm gonna go on ahead, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in the dining hall in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be along in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Rodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, since you were taking so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:47.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Oh! Mamiina!\N— Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, your braids are coming undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll fix them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, we do have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:19.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those Simoun from the Ruins made it to the enemy base ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,But don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You have Morinas as your pair, and she's an excellent auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, if something goes wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be there to protect you, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is only a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:46.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, if we don't fight, nothing bad can happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,That would be best, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,From the information the two of you have gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:06:01.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,we've narrowed down the Argentine base ship's area of operations to this region here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,With only those powerless Simile?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:10.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,the two of us will guard the rear, and relay communications to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:18.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The difference in mobility between the Simile and the Simoun is just too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Creating a mixed unit would be... well, impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,There you go again, Floe, making promises you can't keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Alti started—!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:40.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't we all comrades, who have eaten from the same pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! Mamiina, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh! Uh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please continue, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, first, Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,...should divide into two groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mamiina sure has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,What was that "No! You mustn't!" all about, Ro-do-re?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that Vyura had been doing recon missions in a Simile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:16.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, we mustn't waste Vyura and her partner's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to stand firm as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:32.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, we've reached our assigned deployment area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The operation will proceed as planned. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:50.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is Central Command using Chor Tempest this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:57.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,As Sibylla Dominura correctly pointed out, Central Command doesn't understand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:03.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,It will be quite a while before Chor Tempest returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,This would be a good time for the two of you to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:10.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Resting is part of duty," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right, Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep a sharp eye out for Chor Tempest's return!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Set course for the patrol area. All ahead two thirds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:32.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were forbidden to attend Angulas's funeral, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our country is really terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not so, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,As the situation continues to worsen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:43.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,people fall back on rules and normality to comfort themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, I believe you've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:58.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's all "I am going to detach the speaker cable for a while."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess they're having an "adult conversation" that they don't want the rest of us to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:04.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's a large shadow inside that cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:30.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep the speaker cable attached, and approach from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we found it, so shouldn't we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those Simoun that we saw at the Ruins could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to find out for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:40.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's at least confirm that before we head back, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't let down your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,This area is likely to be heavily patrolled by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,They aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're gonna leave the patrol area soon, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:38.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, shouldn't we head back to the rendezvous point with the regina soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll search this area for a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the {\i1}Messis{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,One Simoun approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Approaching rapidly... It's one of Chor Tempest's Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Aaeru and Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see her on board the {\i1}Messis{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was worried about that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru and Sibylla Yun, please go on ahead.
Comment: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought they'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. We'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:57.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Re-route all power from the helical motors to the engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Set course for the patrol area. All ahead flank!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll head to the rendezvous point with the regina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Got it!\N— Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Withdraw at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Again! Shark Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger! Shark Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't shake them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Damn, they're freakin' quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril just told us... to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to do what Neviril says!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we're both gonna go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry back and tell the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hand on! We'll be right back, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:41.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will not fail you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:03.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can understand my words, listen closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:07.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the sort of person to die in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just another nameless sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't care about my own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:19.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the one who lies behind me is the Simulacrum Theocracy's most revered sibylla,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's going to get out of here safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:28.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,and I won't let you lay a finger on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,She who is behind you and you who are before me are both glorious sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:43.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,The sibyllae of the Holy Land of Simulacrum are the priestesses who dwell closest to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:48.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the Plumbum Highlands, we honour you above all others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:54.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is truly regrettable that we must fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:58.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,We do not wish to capture an injured sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are priestesses of the Plumbum Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are nothing like the soldiers from the Archipelago who man this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:12.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our recent battle is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are no longer called to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, you must trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,If our intention was to capture you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,there would be no need for such complexity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:37.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their words... contain no falsehood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, do this with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:27.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you let us escape from here, you will have nowhere to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:32.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, if {\i1}you{\i0} are captured, you will be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:45.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You all recognized {\i1}me{\i0} as a true sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:51.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you let me escape, you will all be killed as traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:04.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:36.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rather than allow yourself to be murdered by these soldiers, please, allow me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the way things should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:41.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,In your language:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aa-e-ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,AA - E - RU ! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Large aircraft, dead ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sir, it must be the Archipelago's base ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,It appears to be on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,General quarters! All hands, set Condition One throughout the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, set Condition One.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:52.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, brace for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,We will provide support for the priestesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:35.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:37.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Quickly! To the {\i1}Messis{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:38.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Move, Rodoreamon! You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rodoreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:50.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry too, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to get out of here! We need to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:00.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't just stand here doing nothing at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:24.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllaaaaa!
