Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:11.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,A proud sibylla of the Simulacrum Theocracy, and a true young lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:14.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Mamiina... is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:17.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Elegy.
